1. 创建ca证书
    cfssl gencert -initca ca-csr.json | cfssljson -bare ca
2. 创建服务端证书,hostname要指定admission-webhook的svc名称
cfssl gencert -ca=ca.pem -ca-key=ca-key.pem -config=ca-config.json \
		-hostname=admission-resource.default.svc -profile=server server-csr.json | cfssljson -bare server

3. 创建tls的secret
    kubectl create secret tls admission-resource-tls \
            --key=server-key.pem \
            --cert=server.pem
4. 将ca.pem放入admission-webhook的caBundle中
    cat ca.pem|base64
5.编译镜像
    docker build -t haozi4263/admission-resource:v0.9 . && docker push haozi4263/admission-resource:v0.9                                      [15:58:36]
6. 运行admission-webhook
   kubectl apply -f deploy/deploy.yaml
7. 注册admission-webhook
   kubectl apply -f deploy/registry.yaml
8. 运行deployment测试,观察日志
   kubectl apply -f deploy/test/admission-resource.yaml
   Error from server: error when creating "admission-resource-test.yaml": admission webhook "im.shimo.admission-resource" denied the request: limit_cpu/request_cpu: 2000 or limit_mem/limit_cpu: 0 above 4倍

项目说明：
    对deployment/statfulset资源检测limit_cpu/request_cpu和limit_memory/limit_memory
    占比是否大于4倍数，大于4倍以上说明资源分配不合理，拒绝创建deployment/statfulset
    小于4倍则认为合理允许创建deployment/statfulset


    增加去除init container
    增加lables: